descript.abstract: This data displays Indonesia (the islands of Indonesia). It was generated by the World Resources Institute (WRI) from the 2003 District GIS dataset, produced by Badan Pusat Statistik (BPS).
descript.supplinf: This data is provided for display purposes for this Atlas.
